{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "欧雷因 第4话 赌徒的生存意义",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "从刚才开始好像就有不安分的家伙\\n在城堡周围瞎转悠。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "喔，那是……\\n这样啊，打探到这里了吗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喂，欧雷因，\\n你认识那些家伙吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "是街里的流氓无赖。\\n以前游戏上赢过他们，\\n可能我做得有点过头了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "好像就被他们盯上了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "没道理啊。\\n怎么能对按规则游戏的玩家\\n进行这样的恐吓呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "如果真的如你所说，\\n倒也罢了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "欧雷因，\\n你那时又耍诈了吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "你们半斤八两……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "唉……你不如和盘托出，\\n老实道歉怎么样？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "哈哈哈，这次我可没有耍诈啊。\\n再说就算道歉也没用。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "也许是因为我\\n让他在部下面前丢面子了吧？\\n那个头目简直暴跳如雷……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "眼看差点就要被杀，\\n我就慌忙逃跑了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "就因为赌输了吗？\\n那么一说好像是太过分了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "到底发生了什么？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "在闹市，我遇到了一位\\n两眼放光的年轻人。\\n",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "他好像是个很贫穷的演员，\\n第一次被选中担任主角，\\n非常兴奋。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "但是，\\n附近那帮混混的头目\\n却捉弄他。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "我有些看不惯，\\n就和他打赌\\n年轻人的舞台演出是否成功。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "就条件来说，对方有绝对优势。\\n然后我和他约定，如果我赢了，\\n他就要向年轻人下跪道歉。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "然后，结果呢？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "哈哈，舞台表演大获成功！大胜利哦！\\n然后按照约定，让那个头目\\n在街上的广场下跪道歉了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "对混混们心有不满的观众欣喜万分！\\n而且，\\n那个一跃成为明星的年轻人……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "每逢有公演，\\n都会给我送来特等席的票，直至现在。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "原来如此，真感人……\\n但结果不是招人怨恨，\\n被人上门寻仇吗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "是啊。可是不也挺好吗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "这样的话我愿意为年轻人的未来\\n下赌注。\\n这是我人生的价值嘛！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "诶，好像对他刮目相看了。\\n对吧，库菈乌。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "唔、对。算是吧……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "我觉得自己是做了件好事，\\n得罪那些流氓无赖也没办法。\\n不过……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "这次那些家伙的目标，\\n可能不是我呢……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "咦，这是怎么回事？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "呵呵，没什么。\\n到时候就知道了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "欧雷因",
            "context": "大概吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}